          <int-org-section id="IO-COE-1000" sllink="SLSDOC" slsdocrf="INT-ORG-SECTREF">
               <heading>Conference of International Non-Governmental Organizations</heading>
               <p>The Conference gathers more than 300 international non-governmental organizations (INGOs), and aims to provide a bridge between politicians and civil society. It meets twice a year during the ordinary sessions of the Parliamentary Assembly. A President is elected for a three year term.</p>
